item.title: Applying Mock Service Worker (MSW) for Seamless Web Development
item.author: han@d.foundation (Han Ngo)
item.description: Introduction Mock Service Worker (MSW) is an API mocking library that leverages the Service Worker API to intercept requests. It offers unique features that set it apart from traditional mocking libraries, making it a go-to choice for developers.
